"title": "8164: spirituality",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8164: spirituality",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The quality of life generated and nourished by the Spirit of God, in which believers experience the power and presence of God in their lives. True spirituality comes from living under the control of the Holy Spirit and is evidenced by the fruit of the Spirit, spiritual maturity and growth in holiness.</p>\n<h2>The foundations of spirituality</h2>\n<h3>The need for spiritual renewal</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:14\">ROM 7:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:19\">JUD 1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Believers have been renewed spiritually</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:5-John3:8\">JHN 3:5–3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5\">TIT 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3\">1PE 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23\">1PE 1:23</a></p>\n<h3>Faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:53-John6:58\">JHN 6:53–6:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:31\">JHN 20:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:31\">ACT 16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9-Rom10:10\">ROM 10:9–10:10</a></p>\n<h3>A longing for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:8\">PSA 27:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:2\">PSA 119:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:5-Ps143:6\">PSA 143:5–143:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10-Phil3:14\">PHP 3:10–3:14</a></p>\n<h2>The nature of spirituality</h2>\n<h3>Living under the Spirit's control</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:9\">ROM 8:5–8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:12-Rom8:13\">ROM 8:12–8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16-Gal5:17\">GAL 5:16–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18\">EPH 5:18</a></p>\n<h3>Reflecting Jesus Christ's character</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2-1John3:3\">1JN 3:2–3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Intimacy with God through the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14-Rom8:16\">ROM 8:14–8:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>Evidence of spirituality</h2>\n<h3>Bearing spiritual fruit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:17\">MAT 7:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:5-John15:8\">JHN 15:5–15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8-Eph5:9\">EPH 5:8–5:9</a></p>\n<h3>Love for one another</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7\">1JN 4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34-John13:35\">JHN 13:34–13:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:1-1Cor13:4\">1CO 13:1–13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual maturity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:1-1Cor3:3\">1CO 3:1–3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:20\">1CO 14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:13-Heb5:14\">HEB 5:13–5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Showing concern for weaker believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1\">GAL 6:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:1-Rom14:3\">ROM 14:1–14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:19-Rom14:21\">ROM 14:19–14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:9-1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:9–8:13</a></p>\n<h3>Understanding spiritual truths</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:9-1Cor2:13\">1CO 2:9–2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:17\">JHN 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13-John16:15\">JHN 16:13–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:15-1Cor2:16\">1CO 2:15–2:16</a></p>\n<h3>Holiness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:12\">TIT 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:19–6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:24\">GAL 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1-Col3:2\">COL 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:2-1John2:6\">1JN 2:2–2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:2-1John5:3\">1JN 5:2–5:3</a></p>\n<h2>Aids to spirituality</h2>\n<h3>Co-operation with the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:25\">GAL 5:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:51\">ACT 7:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30\">EPH 4:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:19\">1TH 5:19</a></p>\n<h3>Meditation on God's word</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8\">JOS 1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:7\">JHN 17:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:15–3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Spending time with God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12\">LUK 6:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:35\">MRK 1:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:13\">ACT 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>Encouragement of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24\">HEB 10:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:11-1Thess2:12\">1TH 2:11–2:12</a></p>\n<h3>Tests and trials</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:4\">JAS 1:2–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:4\">ROM 5:3–5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:6-1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:6–1:7</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of spirituality</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:24\">GEN 5:24</a> <em>Enoch</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:9\">GEN 6:9</a> <em>Noah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:3\">NUM 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:6-Num12:8\">NUM 12:6–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:14\">1SA 13:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:22\">ACT 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:5\">ACT 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:8\">ACT 6:8</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:24\">ACT 11:24</a> <em>Barnabas</em></p>",
